Package org.ingrahamrobotics.dotnettables

Interface Summary
DotNetTable.DotNetTableEvents The interface necessary to provide callback handling of "change" and "stale" events
 

Class Summary
DotNetTable A named and published or subscribed DotNetTable.
DotNetTables A wrapper for FRC NetworkTables that provides enforced directionality, a unified view of subscribed and published tables, and periodic updates and staleness detection This project also exposes all of the underlying NetworkTables classes, methods, and data types, for easy inclusion in both Java and .NET projects
